# Shopping Trends Analysis (Client Project)

## Objective
To analyze U.S. shopping trends data using SQL and identify customer purchasing patterns and discount opportunities to improve sales.

## Dataset
- U.S. Shopping Trends Dataset
- Includes customer demographics, purchase details, discounts, and product categories

## Key Analysis Performed
- Category-wise purchase analysis
- Impact of discounts on customer purchases
- Customer behavior analysis based on age and gender
- Identification of product categories requiring discounts

## SQL Concepts Used
- SELECT, WHERE
- GROUP BY, HAVING
- CASE statements
- Aggregate functions
- Subqueries

## Tools Used
- MySQL
